snippet.textDisplay:
My dad passed away 2.5 years ago and I miss him so much! I love him more than anything in this world. I have all the materialistic things that I always dreamt of since childhood but nothing brings me happiness. Everything feels incomplete and void. I don't know for how many years I am going to feel this way. Jindagi me itni badi cheez kho di ki kisi cheez milne ki aab khusi nahi! 
But at the end of the day listening to this songs makes me feel little closer to my dad. At 5:12- Teri Laadki mai, Teri laadli mai, kitni bhi dur chahe tujse dur rahu...... Makes me emotional every time. 
I listen to this song every night because maybe only this song can describe how much I love and miss my dad!
